title: Sonic Youth Mix Tapes 1-6 Rarities and b-sides
description:
Compilations put up by Sonic Youth on their own website as streaming audio. I picked them up on individual torrents, but I&#039;m putting them up all together in the hope of increasing their activity.
 <a href="
http://www.sonicyouth.com/jukebox/jukebox.html" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.sonicyouth.com/jukebox/jukebox.html</a> has the current one.

Visit http://www.sonicyouth.com/mustang/sy/ for information on each song. Many were once hard to find rarities and live versions of studio songs that have since been released on either the deluxe editions of certain cds or on the Destroyed Room. Still, nice to have them in their original mix tape setting, and some of these songs haven&#039;t been released elsewhere.

I haven&#039;t been able to complete the download of Mix Tape 5, but I included it here just in case someone with a seed will see this torrent and complete it for us.

Thanks to the original seeders.
